# CUPS filter registration for printer wake pre-filter
# Installed to /usr/share/cups/mime/printserver-wake.convs
#
# This registers a cost-0 filter that runs before all other filters.
# It wakes the USB printer from firmware sleep, then passes data through.
#
# Format: source/type destination/type cost filter
application/vnd.cups-raw application/vnd.cups-raw 0 cups-pre-filter-wake.sh
